{
  "stem": "22944.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The man who was a good friend of my uncle and aunt, Ella and Miklos Fisher, was Gerze Hoffman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I understood he belonged to a Hlinka movement, which was a pro-Nazi movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In spite of that, he did help us not to get on that train, what was quite a miracle to look later at what happened to all the Jews-- actually, a Nazi who saved us that stage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we entered that room-- [NON-ENGLISH] 52-- on a ground-floor flat which was empty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, obviously, people must have known what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, Pernik, Gavalovic, they were working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pernik was the caretaker of the block of flats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gavalovic was-- William Gavalovic was a friend of my uncle who was an accountant in the mill as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I presume there were a few others-- director of the mill knew about-- or they devised a plan how to save my uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They did not plan to save eight people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But Ella was a very close member of her family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For some reason, now, she managed to persuade all these people that Lilly, Seren, Olga, Robby, Gertie, me should be included in this rescue.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, as day by day-- since it got worse, we could not find our father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or at least our father did not reach that stage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he may have known where we are, but we don't really know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All we know is that after a few days, my father appeared the other side of the road, unshaven, without any hat-- and kind of working clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he probably tried to attract attention.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we looked out the window, and he was shouting Olga, Olga!",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
